race.comment: MINTER BLINDER (1) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (24.71) at Sale in a Maiden. Lines up from box 1 for the first time. Capable of going well again. KING OF PAIN (6) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 2 lengths into second (22.98) at this track in a Maiden over 400m. Bold showing expected. PICANHA (8) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Turtle Time (23.57) in a Maiden. Key player if finds best. NATINA (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
